(147,"p")(148,"b"),l(149,"4. SOURCES OF PERSONAL INFORMATION "),k()(),T(150,"ul")(151,"li"),l(152," 4.1 Personal information may be collected from the following sources: "),T(153,"ul")(154,"li"),l(155," directly from the person when he/she applies for any RTMC related employment, provide services to the RTMC, submit forms requests or transactions, use our websites or make use of any of the RTMC services; "),k(),T(156,"li"),l(157," from public registers, credit bureaus and law enforcement agencies and any other organisation from which the RTMC may acquire your information; "),k(),T(158,"li"),l(159," from people and entities employed by the RTMC to provide services to the RTMC which may be legally entitled to provide the RTMC with Personal Information. "),k()()()(),T(160,"p")(161,"b"),l(162,"5. STORAGE OF PERSONAL INFORMATION "),k()(),T(163,"ul")(164,"li"),l(165," All personal information collected by the RTMC will be stored as follows: "),T(166,"ul")(167,"li"),l(168," in a secure and safe manner according to strict information security principles with safeguards to ensure its privacy and confidentiality; "),k(),T(169,"li"),l(170," for no longer than is necessary to achieve the purpose for which it was collected unless further retention is: "),T(171,"ul")(172,"li"),l(173," required by law or contractual obligation; "),k(),T(174,"li"),l(175," otherwise reasonably required by the RTMC for lawful purposes related to its functions and activities; "),k(),T(176,"li"),l(177," retained further with the person\u2019s consent; "),k()()(),T(178,"p"),l(179," after which the information will be de-identified and disposed of as per the RTMC\u2019s relevant Policies. "),k()()()(),T(180,"p")(181,"b"),l(182,"6. SHARING OF PERSONAL INFORMATION "),k()(),T(183,"ul")(184,"li"),l(185," The RTMC will only use Personal Information that you provided through this website for the purposes for which you provided it. "),k(),T(186,"li"),l(187," You agree that that the RTMC may use your Personal Information for the purposes of administering and improving the website improving our services or communication to you. The Personal Information you provide to us may be shared with operators to the extend necessary for them to administer and improve the website on our behalf. "),k(),T(188,"li"),l(189," Any information supplied to the RTMC will be treated as confidential and the RTMC will not disclose information unless legally permitted thereto. No information will be transferred to a Third Party without the explicit consent of the Data Subject unless legally obliged thereto. By providing the personal information, the Data Subject agrees that the RTMC may transfer the information to the following people and organisations in pursuit of the Data Processing purposes: "),T(190,"ul")(191,"li"),l(192," the divisions and units in the RTMC, including directors, Employees, contractors, agents, auditors, legal and other professional advisors who are authorised to process this information; "),k(),T(193,"li"),l(194," financial and government organisations who may request information from the RTMC, in which case the Data Subject will be notified in advance; the provision of such information, including banks, governmental, judicial, regulatory and law enforcement bodies including the South African Revenue services and the National Credit Regulator; "),k(),T(195,"li"),l(196," persons employed by the RTMC to provide services on our behalf and that adhere to principles similar to the RTMC regarding the treatment of Personal Information; "),k(),T(197,"li"),l(198," to any person to whom the RTMC cede, delegate, transfer or assign any of the RTMC\u2019s rights or obligations pertaining to products and/or services provided to the person or contracts concluded with the person; "),k(),T(199,"li"),l(200," to any person who acts as legal guardian, executor of an estate, curator or in a similar capacity; "),k(),T(201,"li"),l(202," to third parties in limited circumstances where authorised by 