 communicate with the RTMC through these services, that social network service may collect your Personal Information for its own purpose. "),k(),T(234,"li"),l(235," These services may track your use of the RTMC\u2019s Website on those pages where their links are displayed. If you are logged into those services (including any Google service) while using the RTMC\u2019s Website, their tracking will be associated with your profile with those service providers. "),k(),T(236,"li"),l(237," These services have their own privacy policies which are independent of the privacy policy and practises of the RTMC. "),k()(),T(238,"p")(239,"b"),l(240,"9. YOUR RIGHTS REGARDING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION "),k()(),T(241,"ul")(242,"li"),l(243," A Data Subject (employee, contractor, supplier and/or customer) has the following rights to his/her Personal Information collected, processed, and stored by the RTMC the right to: "),T(244,"ul")(245,"li"),l(246," access to any Personal Information that the RTMC holds about you; "),k(),T(247,"li"),l(248," the right to rectify or update your Personal Information collected; "),k(),T(249,"li"),l(250," object at any time to the processing of the Personal Information in which event the consequences of the objection will be explained to the Data Subject; "),k(),T(251,"li"),l(252," request the RTMC to no longer process the Personal Information of the Data Subject should the information not be required for further processing or by law; "),k(),T(253,"li"),l(254," request the RTMC to remove from any of the RTMC\u2019s subscription lists at any time. "),k()()()(),T(255,"p")(256,"b"),l(257,"10. GENERAL CONDITIONS PERTAINING TO PERSONAL INFORMATION "),k()(),T(258,"ul")(259,"li"),l(260," The RTMC accepts no liability whatsoever for any loss, damage (whether direct, indirect, special or consequential) and/or expenses of any nature whatsoever which may arise as a result of, or which may be attributable directly or indirectly from information made available on thes